						               													<description>Mechropolis is currently under development.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Mechropolis is a game of adventure, tactical combat, and choose your own adventure-like campaign play.  As added replay value, the game also incorporates a quicker player vs. player combat system included in the base game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Taking place in the turmoil-ridden machine-city of Mechropolis, players assume the role of a mechanical freedom fighter, and travel the land in attempts to unhinge the current regime ruling the city with an iron (literally!) fist.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players will have access to hundreds of items, weapons, skills, powers and upgrades, giving them fully customizable characters to play with.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Two ways to play:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;1)  Follow the &amp;quot;choose your own adventure&amp;quot; style game play in the cooperative campaign and fight against the enemy using tactical combat on a large, interchangeable game board.   Players play against the game itself, no &amp;quot;dungeon master&amp;quot; needed.  While not in combat, player traverse the terrain on the overall city area map, visiting locales, buying/selling scavenged items, and fighting through random encounters.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;2)  Play with or against your friends in player vs. player deathmatch, capture the flag, king of the hill, and other team games for a free for all, fun filled action packed gaming experience.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;If you enjoyed PC games such as the Jagged Alliance series, X-COM, or Fallout: Tactics, you'll enjoy the tactical game play and customizable options in Mechropolis!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;If you like games such as Star Wars: Epic Duals, Frag, and Gunslinger, but wish the game was more epic, strategic, less luck driven and deeper with more replay value, this will be the game for you!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
